% \section{Compilation}
%
% PSTricks generates PostScript code, which standard pdflatex or lualatex compilers cannot process directly. You typically use the following workflow:
%
% \textbf{The DVI $\rightarrow$ PS $\rightarrow$ PDF chain:}
%
% Compile your document using the latex command, followed by dvips, and finally ps2pdf, e.g.,
% \verb|latex file.tex && dvips file.dvi && ps2pdf file.ps|
%